snippet.title: Project-X Longplay (Amiga) [4K]
snippet.description:
Developed and published by Team 17 in 1992

A new recording of this visually stunning shoot 'em up from Team 17. It's insanely difficult, but you can't deny that it's one of the best-looking games on the Amiga! Use the time codes below to skip ahead.

Credits
Coding: Andreas Tadic, Stefan Boberg
Graphics: Rico Holmes
Music: Allister Brimble, Bjørn Lynne

Time Codes:
00:00 - Intro music
05:23 - Level 01
13:40 - Level 02
24:08 - Level 03
31:57 - Level 04
46:12 - Level 05
46:24 - Level 06
48:10 - Ending
